{"title":"Originals \u0026 Triangles","description":"","products":[{"product_id":"honeysticks-originals-12pk","title":"Honeysticks Beeswax Crayons Originals 12pk","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW23206258 BCX8\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eOur \u003cstrong\u003eHoneysticks Beeswax Crayons Originals 12pk\u003c\/strong\u003e are a best-seller for a reason - they're the perfect first crayon. Ideal for toddlers aged 1-3, Originals have a short, stubby design made especially for little hands - easy to grip yet tough to break. Handcrafted from pure New Zealand beeswax, they're a safe, sustainable way to introduce your little artist to a world of pure creation.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eThe perfect first crayon:\u003c\/strong\u003e The unique chubby shape of Honeysticks Originals makes them easier for small hands to hold, but much harder for small hands to break! Each crayon is 55mm long and 20mm in diameter.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eNatural + food-grade ingredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Handmade using 100% pure New Zealand beeswax and food-grade pigments for colour. Non-toxic and safe for toddlers and children, with no paraffin wax or cheap fillers.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eSustainable and low impact:\u003c\/strong\u003e The beeswax used to create Honeysticks is a natural by-product of honey production. This sustainable process causes minimal impact on the environment and gives the crayons a wonderful honey scent.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003e12 exciting colours:\u003c\/strong\u003e Get creative and explore! Our food-grade colours easily bond to the paper, posters or artboard.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eHandcrafted by families, for families: \u003c\/strong\u003eDesigned by parents who believe in a better way to play, Honeysticks Originals are handmade in New Zealand to inspire creativity from the very first scribble.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eNow, in our refreshed Honeysticks look - welcome to a world of pure creation!\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/em\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Honeysticks UK","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":56350549213565,"sku":"HCROR12","price":17.95,"currency_code":"GBP","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0553\/5465\/4896\/files\/Originals12pk.png?v=1765163773"},{"product_id":"honeysticks-originals-pastel-12pk","title":"Honeysticks Beeswax Crayons Originals Pastel 12pk","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW237023030 BCX8\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW139955204 BCX8\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW180185860 BCX8\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eOur \u003cstrong\u003eHoneysticks Beeswax Crayons Originals Pastel 12pk\u003c\/strong\u003e are a best-seller for a reason - they're the perfect first crayon. Ideal for toddlers aged 1-3, Originals have a short, stubby design made especially for little hands - easy to grip yet tough to break. Handcrafted from pure New Zealand beeswax, they're a safe, sustainable way to introduce your little artist to a world of pure creation.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eThe perfect first crayon:\u003c\/strong\u003e The unique chubby shape of Honeysticks Originals makes them easier for small hands to hold, but much harder for small hands to break! Each crayon is 55mm long and 20mm in diameter.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eNatural + food-grade ingredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Handmade using 100% pure New Zealand beeswax and food-grade pigments for colour. Non-toxic and safe for toddlers and children, with no paraffin wax or cheap fillers.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eSustainable and low impact:\u003c\/strong\u003e The beeswax used to create Honeysticks is a natural by-product of honey production. This sustainable process causes minimal impact on the environment and gives the crayons a wonderful honey scent.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan class=\"TextRun SCXW126418118 BCX8\" lang=\"EN-NZ\" data-contrast=\"none\"\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-parastyle=\"Normal (Web)\" class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW126418118 BCX8\"\u003e12 beautiful, pastel shades:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan class=\"TextRun SCXW126418118 BCX8\" lang=\"EN-NZ\" data-contrast=\"none\"\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-parastyle=\"Normal (Web)\" class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW126418118 BCX8\"\u003e Cooling shades for dreamy creations! Our food-grade colours easily bond to the paper, \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-parastyle=\"Normal (Web)\" class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW126418118 BCX8\"\u003eposters\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-parastyle=\"Normal (Web)\" class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW126418118 BCX8\"\u003e or artboard.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-props='{\"134233117\":false,\"134233118\":false,\"201341983\":0,\"335559738\":0,\"335559739\":0,\"335559740\":240}' class=\"EOP SCXW126418118 BCX8\"\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eHandcrafted by families, for families: \u003c\/strong\u003eDesigned by parents who believe in a better way to play, Honeysticks Originals are handmade in New Zealand to inspire creativity from the very first scribble.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eNow, in our refreshed Honeysticks look - welcome to a world of pure creation!\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/em\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Honeysticks UK","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":56350549311869,"sku":"HCRORP12","price":17.95,"currency_code":"GBP","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0553\/5465\/4896\/files\/ORIP_1.png?v=1765225318"},{"product_id":"honeysticks-super-jumbos-6pk","title":"Honeysticks Beeswax Crayons Super Jumbos 6pk","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW231400276 BCX8\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW89954478 BCX8\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBig, bold, and made for little hands – \u003cstrong\u003eHoneysticks Beeswax Crayons Super Jumbos 6pk\u003c\/strong\u003e are a perfect next step in your toddler’s creative journey. These super-sized crayons help build grip strength and coordination, making them ideal for curious creators aged 1 and up.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eSuper-sized for little hands: \u003c\/strong\u003eAt 10cm long and 2cm thick, these chunky crayons are easy to hold and hard to break – perfect for building early drawing confidence.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eNo nasties, just pure creativity: \u003c\/strong\u003eCrafted using 100% pure New Zealand beeswax and food-grade colours. No paraffin wax, no fillers, no worries.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eBetter for them, better for the planet:\u003c\/strong\u003e With sustainably sourced beeswax and natural + non-toxic ingredients, Honeysticks are gentle on little ones and the earth.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eHandcrafted by families, for families:\u003c\/strong\u003e Designed by parents who believe in a better way to play, Honeysticks Super Jumbos are lovingly handmade in New Zealand to encourage creative expression from the very first scribble. \u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eNow, in our refreshed Honeysticks look – welcome to a world of pure creation.\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/em\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Honeysticks UK","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":56350549705085,"sku":"HCRSJ6","price":14.95,"currency_code":"GBP","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0553\/5465\/4896\/files\/SJ6pk_6.png?v=1765225865"},{"product_id":"honeysticks-triangles-10pk","title":"Honeysticks Beeswax Crayons Triangles 10pk","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW216363052 BCX8\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW175986420 BCX8\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan lang=\"EN-US\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSay hello to our easy-grip, no-roll crayons!\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan lang=\"EN-US\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHoneysticks Beeswax Crayons Triangles 10pk\u003c\/strong\u003e are a fun and functional next step for toddlers developing their fine motor skills. With their clever triangular shape and fun colours (made safer), they’re perfect for artists aged one and above.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003c!-- [if !supportLists]--\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eEasy-grip triangular shape: \u003c\/strong\u003eThe perfect beginner crayon — 5.5cm long and 2cm wide, shaped for developing grips and made to stay put on the table.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eNo nasties, just pure creativity:\u003c\/strong\u003e Crafted using 100% pure New Zealand beeswax. No paraffin wax, no fillers, no worries.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eGentle on the earth: \u003c\/strong\u003eThe beeswax used to create Honeysticks is a natural by-product of honey production. This sustainable process has a minimal impact on the environment and imparts a wonderful honey scent to the crayons.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003e8 exciting colours: \u003c\/strong\u003eGet creative and explore! Our food-grade colours easily bond to paper, posters, or artboards.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eHandcrafted by families, for families: \u003c\/strong\u003eDesigned by parents who believe in a better way to play, Honeysticks Triangles are handmade in New Zealand to inspire creativity from the very first scribble. \u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan lang=\"EN-US\"\u003eNow, in our refreshed Honeysticks look – welcome to a world of pure creation!\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/em\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Honeysticks UK","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":56350549836157,"sku":"HCRTR10","price":17.95,"currency_code":"GBP","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0553\/5465\/4896\/files\/HCRTR10.webp?v=1765226201"},{"product_id":"honeysticks-bath-crayon-triangles-10pk","title":"Honeysticks Bath Crayons Triangles 10pk","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"SCXW222297252 BCX8\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW222297252 BCX8\"\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"p1\"\u003eTriangular crayons for tub-time creativity. \u003cstrong\u003eHoneysticks Bath Crayon Triangles 10pk\u003c\/strong\u003e are the perfect first step into bath-time art. With their clever triangle shape, they’re easy to grip, won’t roll away, and are made with pure beeswax and soy wax for safe, sensory play.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul class=\"ul1\"\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"li1\"\u003e\n\u003cspan class=\"s1\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cb\u003eShaped for small hands:\u003c\/b\u003e The triangle design encourages grip development and early mark-making – perfect for little artists just getting started. Plus, it won’t roll off the tub mid-play. When they’re ready for the next stage, try our Honeysticks Bath Crayon Super Jumbos.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"li1\"\u003e\n\u003cspan class=\"s1\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cb\u003eCreative confidence, built in the bath:\u003c\/b\u003e Support sensory learning, coordination and imagination, all while making a splash.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"li1\"\u003e\n\u003cspan class=\"s1\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cb\u003eTen vibrant colours to explore:\u003c\/b\u003e For drawing, doodling, and colour-filled fun that washes off when the fun is done.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"li1\"\u003e\n\u003cspan class=\"s1\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cb\u003eNo nasties, just pure creativity:\u003c\/b\u003e Crafted with natural beeswax and soy wax, plus food-grade colourants. Safe for play, safe for planet.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"li1\"\u003e\n\u003cspan class=\"s1\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cb\u003eWipes clean with warm water:\u003c\/b\u003e No scrubbing needed – a gentle wipe and the tub is ready for next time.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"li1\"\u003e\n\u003cspan class=\"s1\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cb\u003eLovingly handmade in New Zealand:\u003c\/b\u003e Created by parents who believe in a better way to play – safe, sustainable, and designed to inspire from the very first splash.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"p1\"\u003e\u003cem\u003e\u003cb\u003eNow in our refreshed Honeysticks look – welcome to a world of pure creation!\u003c\/b\u003e\u003c\/em\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Honeysticks UK","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":56350550262141,"sku":"HBTTR10","price":17.95,"currency_code":"GBP","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0553\/5465\/4896\/files\/Bath-Crayons2_2dcc4a48-2928-4de6-b1e9-d88a11b86876.png?v=1765336282"}],"url":"https:\/\/honeysticks.co.uk\/collections\/originals-triangles.oembed","provider":"Honeysticks UK","version":"1.0","type":"link"}